casebody.data:
No. 10-10675 (10A1153). Donald Edward Beaty, Petitioner v. Janice K. Brewer, Governor of Arizona, et al. 563 U.S. 1018, 131 S. Ct. 2929,

179 L. Ed. 2d 1267,

2011 U.S. LEXIS 4015. May 25, 2011.

Application for stay of execution of sentence of death, presented to Justice Kennedy, and by him referred to the Court, denied. Petition for writ of certiorari denied.

Same case below, 649 F.3d 1071.
